The paper deals with the construction and analysis of codes, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also involves computations and algorithms, which could fall under cryptography and security (cs.CR) or numerical analysis (cs.NA). The use of cyclotomic cosets and double circulant codes suggests a connection to algebraic combinatorics (cs.DM) and coding theory (cs.CC).
